<!-- ===================== OVERVIEW ===================== -->
<div class="section" style="padding-top:26px;">
  <div class="container-ati">
    <div class="grid" style="grid-template-columns:1.5fr 1fr;gap:30px;align-items:start;">
      <div>
        <h3 style="color:#fff;margin-bottom:14px;">A Centre of Excellence in Technological Education</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:14px;">
          The Advanced Technological Institute (ATI), Badulla is a leading state higher-education
          institute affiliated to the Sri Lanka Institute of Advanced Technological Education
          (SLIATE) under the Ministry of Higher Education. Located in the heart of the Uva Province,
          the institute provides nationally recognised Higher National Diplomas (HND) and a range of
          certificate programmes designed to meet the demands of a rapidly evolving job market.
        </p>
        <p style="color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:14px;">
          Since its establishment, ATI Badulla has been committed to producing competent,
          employable and ethical graduates. Our programmes blend strong academic foundations with
          practical, industry-focused training, supported by experienced lecturers, modern
          laboratories and active links with the professional world.
        </p>
        <p style="color:var(--muted);">
          We take pride in widening access to quality higher education for students of the Uva
          region and beyond, empowering them to build successful careers in information technology,
          accountancy, English and management.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-ati">
        <h3>At a Glance</h3>
        <ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:8px 0 0;color:var(--muted);line-height:2.1;">
          <li>&#127979; Affiliated to SLIATE</li>
          <li>&#127891; Higher National Diplomas &amp; Certificates</li>
          <li>&#128205; Badulla, Uva Province, Sri Lanka</li>
          <li>&#128101; Experienced academic staff</li>
          <li>&#128187; Modern IT &amp; language labs</li>
          <li>&#129309; Strong industry partnerships</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

